nsparent","index":"b1D","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Websocket event\n\nsent from client\n- joinChat ()\n- sendMessage ()\n\nReceive From server\n- receiveMessage ()\n- \n","height":250,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1617053252,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":8,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":1443.5171281999742,"angle":0,"y":-2182.8025931680618,"width":209},{"seed":1702554748,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"NyGEudL9D_J30UaLgARKE","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772704418409,"locked":false,"text":"Chat Database\n\n- Chats\n    — id ( pk, unique )\n    - name\n    - ...metadata\n\n    —— clustered index on id\n    —— no need of secondary indexes\n\n- ChatParticipants\n    - chatId\n    - participantId\n\n    —— (chatId, participantId) clustered index = fast lookups by chatId (e.g., listing participants in a chat).\n    —— Extra index on participantId = fast lookups by participant (e.g., listing chats a user belongs to).\n    —— Both together = efficient for all common access patterns.","version":243,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b1E","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Chat Database\n\n- Chats\n    — id ( pk, unique )\n    - name\n    - ...metadata\n\n    —— clustered index on id\n    —— no need of secondary indexes\n\n- ChatParticipants\n    - chatId\n    - participantId\n\n    —— (chatId, participantId) clustered index = fast lookups by chatId (e.g., listing participants in a chat).\n    —— Extra index on participantId = fast lookups by participant (e.g., listing chats a user belongs to).\n    —— Both together = efficient for all common access patterns.","height":425,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":41889788,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":8,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElemen